<TEXT>
* HUNTLY and Caledonian Thistle have agreed compensation for former
Manchester United player Steve Paterson. The Huntly manager has won a
championship titles with his previous three clubs, Forres as a player,
Elgin and Huntly.
Former Leicester City, Everton and Scotland midfielder Ian Wilson,
recently returned from Japan, and ex-West Ham and Scotland defender Ray
Stewart are two possible candidates for the Huntly vacancy.
</TEXT>
