<TEXT>
IT was interesting to note Mr Alex Salmond's concern for the
discrimination against Roman Catholics in monarchal and British state
affairs (April 29).
Mr Salmond's declared aim is for a separate Scotland. This implies he
has no love for the Union or the monarchy.
It is, therefore, difficult to understand his desire to involve a
