<TEXT>
MISS Carol Stewart, 27, was accused at Inverness Sheriff Court
yesterday of wilfully setting fire to her home in a block of flats at
Glendoe Terrace, Merkinch, Inverness, on Wednesday night, and placing
people in neighbouring flats in danger. The case was continued without
plea until June 1 for a psychiatric report.
</TEXT>
