<TEXT>
A FISHING boat skipper who breached quota regulations was fined #6500
yesterday at Wick. Robert Mitchell, 36, admitted under-declaring 2400kg
of saithe he caught and landed in Scrabster after a trip in the
Banff-registered Mizpah.
